description: Good To Go Juice Truck specializes in organic, locally sourced, fresh pressed juice, smoothies, and salads.  Our farm to sidewalk juice and smoothie truck has found home in Ventura County. Good To Go is focused on providing a healthy fast food alternative for people on the go.  We aim for minimal waste, compost all of our juice waste, and encourage our customers to bring us their reusable containers for their juices and smoothies.   Whether you are an experienced juicer or someone looking to try something new you are sure to find a healthy, delicious treat on our menu.
name: Good To Go Juice Truck
